{"tid":2016435,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[真係笑話]李力持倡 DIY 記協記者證　記協：或涉刑事不排除報警","createTime":"2020-05-14T11:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T11:59:43.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e33272d5c9d947f4a7c72bf6c906b45903e125f3","tid":2016435,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"警方及建制派人士經常批評本港出現「假記者」，導演李力持今日在 Facebook 上載香港記者協會的記者證樣本，並稱「邊位想做記者可以自己 DIY」。香港記者協會今日發聲明，指有人在社交平台上載記者證樣本的圖片，並涉嫌教唆他人偽造記協記者證，引起公眾誤會。記協嚴厲譴責有關行為，由於事件可能涉及刑事罪行，現正尋求法律意見，不排除報警處理，並保留一切法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n記協重申，只有協會的「正式會員」，才有資格申請記協記者證，根據記協會章，要獲得「正式會員」資格，必須以新聞工作為主要收入來源，即受僱於本港傳媒或在港從事傳媒工作，或從事職前和在職新聞工作訓練等，有關申請亦經過該會嚴格審核。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0a52cc36-495a-4ec3-8d64-55bee4808e62_LaGfa_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0a52cc36-495a-4ec3-8d64-55bee4808e62_LaGfa_1200x0.jpeg&h=297065fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"792dff99be1281a60c18503ab7d68561a8a29c29","tid":2016435,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7l%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=9e630c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會三不投聯署</span></span></strong> 就黎deadline<br />\n簽完就share埋俾你身邊既親朋戚友一齊簽啦！！"},{"pid":"43b7fd00f993673823cd5111b1fb8774b56505ab","tid":2016435,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%81%E5%80%A1-diy-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%AD%89-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94-%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%